{"tid":1152613,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透]根本正常男人最後都會揀趙敏","createTime":"2019-05-13T05:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T13:43:38.000Z","uid":58335,"like":55,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"75e04d12eb5b2a86c62909e70b58578e80ecb34d","tid":1152613,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:49:38.000Z","msg":"首先講明，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我愛祝緒丹</span></span><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">，都愛陳鈺琪</span></span>！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysCybew.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysCybew.gif&h=d88ae886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見近日又有周趙大戰<br />\n論樣，趙敏同周芷若真係難分高下<br />\n但趙敏實在為張無忌做得太多嘢<br />\n為左張無忌可以同敵人同歸於盡<br />\n又會去救張無忌<br />\n最重要係為咗張無忌放棄成個元朝<br />\n呢種女人去邊搵？<br />\n<br />\n相反周芷若為左師門同師父不斷去呃張又陷害趙敏<br />\n唔肯放棄<br />\n自從佢落手殺蛛兒已經冇得返轉頭<br />\n之後有幾惡毒已經唔再講<br />\n佢真係變左妖女<br />\n<br />\n但故事還故事<br />\n現實有幾多個趙敏？甘願放棄一切去愛一個人？<br />\n現實大多人都會為錢、事業、名利等放棄愛情， 甚至變得好可怕<br />\n<br />\n現實有好多周芷若， 趙敏很少<br />\n所以我哋先會覺得趙敏完美好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4s5Dnqo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4s5Dnqo.gif&h=420e944e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQC6wiY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQC6wiY.gif&h=ca6f0920&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"256af1b742e450fde1a94a706958c3a727656f60","tid":1152613,"uid":49336,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"當時中國同蒙古係對立<br />\n張無忌揀佢 等住香港人娶隻大陸雞"},{"pid":"afb8173465630b9fd1363bca3efa6dbe5ea5d24d","tid":1152613,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"咪一樣比我波台田伯光溝曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10d1e